gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e677ccf94b9f618ac9e0b34312ef77ca37c8049","tid":1131910,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"abaf42f2dd747f4934c97ab55266fdb4e389ad2b","tid":1131910,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"淨係樓市都唔止"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓市關撚獨立關稅區事咩<br />\n係香港人、支那人天性喜磚，香港又地細，自然炒得起<br />\n你睇下澳洲、加拿大溫哥華，全部都係香港、支那首選移民國家城市，樓價都炒到去世界top5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家亞太區落腳位首選新加坡、東京、首爾，香港如果唔係同支那有親應該唔會有人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落腳香港個成本高到9彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人工、租金隨時全亞洲最高成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9c2222e4289411c25edab1192204afa2eabebfc","tid":1131910,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:21:09.000Z","msg":"香港負責借錢畀一帶一路窮國買強國貨，到時壞賬風險又有幾多億呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea897583da99096b8ba4a647f97bab4b5a43b95","tid":1131910,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9068be34b5f41b7c128d905ca5d8f760be0e2493","tid":1131910,"uid":27451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"奶共都做到教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:57:08.000Z","msg":"好多都奶架依家"},{"pid":"1f5d423374a7968c21870d4ffda3b5f518d411a0","tid":1131910,"u